content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Hyeraph

Hyeraph is a term that appears in Sin'keth's diary. It appears to be a rank within the Dagon'hai. The only known person that was a Hyeraph is Sin'keth Magis who presumably went to on to become High Elder at a later date. The role seems to revolve around leading an incantation of some type, although the nature of it is unknown.
